org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT roles.* FROM roles INNER JOIN member_roles ON member_roles.role_id = roles.id INNER JOIN members ON members.id = member_roles.member_id INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND members.user_id = 2
